8]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 56\n| 20\n| 18\n| 38\n| 36\n| 7\n| 1\n| 2\n| 3\n| 6\n|- \n| [[2008\u201309 SM-liiga season|2008\u201309]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 34\n| 13\n| 12\n| 25\n| 28\n| 2\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n|- bgcolor=\"#f0f0f0\"\n| [[2009\u201310 DEL season|2009\u201310]]\n| [[Hamburg Freezers]]\n| [[Deutsche Eishockey Liga|DEL]]\n| 32\n| 14\n| 5\n| 19\n| 35\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|- \n| [[2009\u201310 SM-liiga season|2009\u201310]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 18\n| 8\n| 6\n| 14\n| 6\n| 5\n| 0\n| 4\n| 4\n| 4\n|- bgcolor=\"#f0f0f0\"\n| [[2010\u201311 SM-liiga season|2010\u201311]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 59\n| 24\n| 27\n| 51\n| 20\n| 16\n| 5\n| 7\n| 12\n| 10\n|- \n| [[2011\u201312 SM-liiga season|2011\u201312]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 50\n| 14\n| 26\n| 40\n| 26\n| 4\n| 0\n| 1\n| 1\n| 0\n|- bgcolor=\"#f0f0f0\"\n| [[2012\u201313 SM-liiga season|2012\u201313]]\n| HIFK\n| SM-l\n| 51\n| 6\n| 13\n| 19\n| 22\n| 7\n| 2\n| 3\n| 5\n| 0\n|- bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\"\n! colspan=\"3\" | SM-l totals\n! 730\n! 249\n! 231\n! 480\n! 329\n! 81\n! 20\n! 20\n! 40\n! 28\n|}\n\n==References==\n<references />\n*{{hockeydb|34179}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100326172058/http://www.sm-liiga.fi/pelaajat/09-10/hifk/kuhta-kimmo.html] (in Finnish)\n*{{eliteprospects|4216}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Ville Peltonen]] | title = Winner of the [[Raimo Kilpi\u00f6 trophy]] | years = 2003-04 | after = [[Jani Rita]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kuhta, Kimmo}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:SC Bern players]]\n[[Category:Finnish ice hockey right wingers]]\n[[Category:Espoo Blues players]]\n[[Category:Hamburg Freezers players]]\n[[Category:HIFK (ice hockey) players]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki]]\n\n\n{{Finland-icehockey-winger-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox ice hockey player \n| image =Kimmo_Kuhta_of_HIFK_-_20110418.jpg\n| image_size = 230px\n| team= \n| league = [[SM-liiga]]\n| played_for = [[HIFK (ice hockey