ale of 67 year old who was confirmed as positive on March 17. The second and the third are from [[Bangalore|Bengaluru]] of age 39 and 21 years respectively. While the former returned from [[Amsterdam]], [[Netherlands|The Netherlands]] on 19 March and the latter from [[Scotland]] on 17 March. The fourth, a 32-year-old man with travel history to [[Mecca]] from [[Gauribidanur]] in [[Chikkaballapura district|Chikkaballapura]].<ref name=\":13\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/state/top-karnataka-stories/man-from-gauribidanur-in-karnataka-tests-positive-for-coronavirus-816011.html|title=Man from Gauribidanur in Karnataka tests positive for coronavirus|date=2020-03-19|website=Deccan Herald|language=en|access-date=2020-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321124652/https://www.deccanherald.com/state/top-karnataka-stories/man-from-gauribidanur-in-karnataka-tests-positive-for-coronavirus-816011.html|archive-date=21 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> The fifth, is a 35-year-old male from Mysore who arrived at [[Bangalore|Bengaluru]] on 19 March from [[Dubai]].<ref name=\":14\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.prajavani.net/district/bengaluru-city/5-cases-in-one-day-714221.html|title=\u0c92\u0c82\u0ca6\u0cc7 \u0ca6\u0cbf\u0ca8 5 \u0caa\u0ccd\u0cb0\u0c95\u0cb0\u0ca3|date=2020-03-22|website=Prajavani|language=en|access-date=2020-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322004528/https://www.prajavani.net/district/bengaluru-city/5-cases-in-one-day-714221.html|archive-date=22 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\":15\">{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://karunadu.karnataka.gov.in/hfw/kannada/nCovDocs/21-03-2020(English).pdf|title=MEDIA BULLETIN: Till date Twenty COVID-19 positive cases have been confirmed in the state which includes one death|date=|work=GOVERNMENT OF KARNATAKA, DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND FAMILY WELFARE SERVICES,BENGALURU|access-date=|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322004528/https://karunadu.karnatak