rand Officer'') (1940)<ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.se/books?id=wXE5AQAAIAAJ&pg=RA2-PA95&hl=sv&source=gbs_selected_pages&cad=2#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Sveriges statskalender f\u00f6r \u00e5ret 1941 |year=1941 |publisher=Fritzes offentliga publikationer |location=Uppsala |language=Swedish |page=272}}</ref>\n*[[File:EST Order of the Cross of the Eagle 3rd Class BAR.png|50px]] {{flag|Estonia}} Third Class of the [[Order of the Cross of the Eagle]] (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:Legion Honneur Commandeur ribbon.svg|50px]] {{flag|France}} Commander of the [[Legion of Honour]] (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:Legion Honneur Officier ribbon.svg|50px]] {{flag|France}} Officer of the [[Legion of Honour]] (between 1931 and 1935)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal31Genstab\"/>\n*[[File:LVA Order of the Three Stars - Commander BAR.png|50px]] {{flag|Latvia}} Commander of the [[Order of the Three Stars]] (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:NLD Order of Orange-Nassau - Commander BAR.png|50px]] {{flag|Netherlands}} Commander of the [[Order of Orange-Nassau]] with swords (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:POL Polonia Restituta Komandorski BAR.svg|50px]] {{flag|Poland}} Commander Second Class of the [[Order of Polonia Restituta]] (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:OK Exceptional Service Medal.png|50px]] {{flag|Kingdom of Hungary}} Commander of the [[Order of Merit of the Republic of Hungary]] (between 1935 and 1940)<ref name=\"Statskal35\"/><ref name=\"Statkal40Genstabk\"/>\n*[[File:PRU Order of Crown ribbon.svg|50px]] {{flag|Prussia}} Knight Fourth Class of the [[Order of the Crown (Prussia)|Order of the Crown]] (1909)<ref>{{cite book |url=